Projects

Weather App

The weather app has been created using React.js, JavaScript, and Bootstrap.On entering the city and country, its weather will be displayed. A Weather API from the OpenWeatherMap was used to gather information. The information from the API helps in displaying the weather conditions that include overall temperature, min temperature, max temperature and weather types such as sunny, windy, rainy, cloudy or thunderstorm.

Lets's Talk

Lets Talk is a website for people facing mental health issues. We in a team of 4 created this for techtoegther2019(Hackathon). To use the resources theyll have to sign up and tell us regarding the issues. After which we give recommendations. In apps resource, there are links to various apps they can access. We used Google books API integrated with UI to give recommendations for books. Videos were shown using the iframe. Chatbot was created using IBM Watson.

City Crime Management

We developed a swing application wherein a citizen can directly report a case without disclosing his/her identity. In this application demonstrated ecosystem model using a singleton design pattern. All the data like cases and location was stored using the ArrayList and Linked list. We also implemented features like a pie chart, email and choosing a date through JFreeChart, JavaMail API, and date chooser.
